{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1267,"text":"Allow me to start this talk with a question to everyone."},{"time":5795,"text":"You know that all over the world,"},{"time":8057,"text":"people fight for their freedom,"},{"time":10852,"text":"fight for their rights."},{"time":13058,"text":"Some battle oppressive governments."},{"time":16219,"text":"Others battle oppressive societies."},{"time":20955,"text":"Which battle do you think is harder?"},{"time":24811,"text":"Allow me to try to answer this question"},{"time":27283,"text":"in the few coming minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30363,"text":"Let me take you back two years ago in my life."},{"time":36179,"text":"It was the bedtime of my son, Aboody."},{"time":39135,"text":"He was five at the time."},{"time":41819,"text":"After finishing his bedtime rituals,"},{"time":44259,"text":"he looked at me and he asked a question:"},{"time":48341,"text":"\"Mommy, are we bad people?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":51572,"text":"I was shocked."},{"time":54032,"text":"\"Why do you say such things, Aboody?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":57189,"text":"Earlier that day, I noticed some bruises"},{"time":59524,"text":"on his face when he came from school."},{"time":62107,"text":"He wouldn't tell me what happened."},{"time":64073,"text":"[But now] he was ready to tell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68136,"text":"\"Two boys hit me today in school."},{"time":70947,"text":"They told me, 'We saw your mom on Facebook."},{"time":74316,"text":"You and your mom should be put in jail.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":79102,"text":"I've never been afraid to tell Aboody anything."},{"time":82243,"text":"I've been always a proud woman of my achievements."},{"time":86947,"text":"But those questioning eyes of my son"},{"time":89162,"text":"were my moment of truth,"},{"time":91987,"text":"when it all came together."},{"time":95740,"text":"You see, I'm a Saudi woman who had been put in jail"},{"time":100158,"text":"for driving a car in a country"},{"time":102293,"text":"where women are not supposed to drive cars."},{"time":107248,"text":"Just for giving me his car keys,"},{"time":109639,"text":"my own brother was detained twice,"},{"time":113495,"text":"and he was harassed to the point he had"},{"time":115108,"text":"to quit his job as a geologist,"},{"time":117096,"text":"leave the country with his wife and two-year-old son."},{"time":120430,"text":"My father had to sit in a Friday sermon"},{"time":122528,"text":"listening to the imam condemning women drivers"},{"time":126200,"text":"and calling them prostitutes"},{"time":128168,"text":"amongst tons of worshippers,"},{"time":130504,"text":"some of them our friends and family of my own father."},{"time":134816,"text":"I was faced with an organized defamation campaign"},{"time":138400,"text":"in the local media combined with false rumors"},{"time":141382,"text":"shared in family gatherings, in the streets"},{"time":144240,"text":"and in schools."},{"time":146984,"text":"It all hit me."},{"time":149328,"text":"It came into focus that those kids"},{"time":151522,"text":"did not mean to be rude to my son."},{"time":153816,"text":"They were just influenced by the adults around them."},{"time":157886,"text":"And it wasn't about me, and it wasn't a punishment"},{"time":161355,"text":"for taking the wheel and driving a few miles."},{"time":165169,"text":"It was a punishment for daring to challenge"},{"time":168018,"text":"the society's rules."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171715,"text":"But my story goes beyond this moment of truth of mine."},{"time":176252,"text":"Allow me to give you a briefing"},{"time":180048,"text":"about my story."},{"time":182240,"text":"It was May, 2011,"},{"time":184276,"text":"and I was complaining to a work colleague"},{"time":186235,"text":"about the harassments I had to face"},{"time":188069,"text":"trying to find a ride back home,"},{"time":189857,"text":"although I have a car and an international driver's license."},{"time":193341,"text":"As long as I've known, women in Saudi Arabia"},{"time":195466,"text":"have been always complaining about the ban,"},{"time":197952,"text":"but it's been 20 years since anyone"},{"time":200368,"text":"tried to do anything about it,"},{"time":202400,"text":"a whole generation ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204600,"text":"He broke the good/bad news in my face."},{"time":206736,"text":"\"But there is no law banning you from driving.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":209893,"text":"I looked it up, and he was right."},{"time":212097,"text":"There wasn't an actual law in Saudi Arabia."},{"time":214776,"text":"It was just a custom and traditions"},{"time":216916,"text":"that are enshrined in rigid religious fatwas"},{"time":220932,"text":"and imposed on women."},{"time":222936,"text":"That realization ignited the idea of June 17,"},{"time":226024,"text":"where we encouraged women to take the wheel"},{"time":228465,"text":"and go drive."},{"time":231193,"text":"It was a few weeks later, we started receiving all these"},{"time":235048,"text":"\"Man wolves will rape you if you go and drive.\""},{"time":238254,"text":"A courageous woman, her name is Najla Hariri,"},{"time":240920,"text":"she's a Saudi woman in the city of Jeddah,"},{"time":243520,"text":"she drove a car and she announced"},{"time":245134,"text":"but she didn't record a video."},{"time":246863,"text":"We needed proof."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248723,"text":"So I drove. I posted a video on YouTube."},{"time":251584,"text":"And to my surprise,"},{"time":253495,"text":"it got hundreds of thousands of views the first day."},{"time":256384,"text":"What happened next, of course?"},{"time":258090,"text":"I started receiving threats"},{"time":259984,"text":"to be killed, raped, just to stop this campaign."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264546,"text":"The Saudi authorities remained very quiet."},{"time":268158,"text":"That really creeped us out."},{"time":270338,"text":"I was in the campaign with other Saudi women"},{"time":272465,"text":"and even men activists."},{"time":274418,"text":"We wanted to know how the authorities"},{"time":276882,"text":"would respond on the actual day, June 17,"},{"time":280490,"text":"when women go out and drive."},{"time":282219,"text":"So this time I asked my brother"},{"time":284277,"text":"to come with me and drive by a police car."},{"time":286368,"text":"It went fast. We were arrested,"},{"time":289122,"text":"signed a pledge not to drive again, released."},{"time":292806,"text":"Arrested again, he was sent to detention for one day,"},{"time":296018,"text":"and I was sent to jail."},{"time":298281,"text":"I wasn't sure why I was sent there,"},{"time":299906,"text":"because I didn't face any charges in the interrogation."},{"time":303083,"text":"But what I was sure of was my innocence."},{"time":305370,"text":"I didn't break a law, and I kept my abaya"},{"time":307835,"text":"— it's a black cloak we wear in Saudi Arabia before we leave the house —"},{"time":311711,"text":"and my fellow prisoners kept asking me to take it off,"},{"time":314693,"text":"but I was so sure of my innocence, I kept saying,"},{"time":317366,"text":"\"No, I'm leaving today.\""},{"time":319591,"text":"Outside the jail, the whole country went into a frenzy,"},{"time":323047,"text":"some attacking me badly,"},{"time":325351,"text":"and others supportive and even collecting signatures"},{"time":329076,"text":"in a petition to be sent to the king to release me."},{"time":333319,"text":"I was released after nine days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335103,"text":"June 17 comes."},{"time":337789,"text":"The streets were packed with police cars"},{"time":340479,"text":"and religious police cars,"},{"time":342640,"text":"but some hundred brave Saudi women"},{"time":344943,"text":"broke the ban and drove that day."},{"time":346975,"text":"None were arrested. We broke the taboo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350063,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360407,"text":"So I think by now, everyone knows that we can't drive,"},{"time":363799,"text":"or women are not allowed to drive, in Saudi Arabia,"},{"time":365984,"text":"but maybe few know why."},{"time":368282,"text":"Allow me to help you answer this question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370866,"text":"There was this official study"},{"time":374002,"text":"that was presented to the Shura Council --"},{"time":376046,"text":"it's the consultative council appointed"},{"time":378310,"text":"by the king in Saudi Arabia —"},{"time":380293,"text":"and it was done by a local professor,"},{"time":382334,"text":"a university professor."},{"time":383652,"text":"He claims it's done based on a UNESCO study."},{"time":388015,"text":"And the study states,"},{"time":391007,"text":"the percentage of rape, adultery,"},{"time":394799,"text":"illegitimate children, even drug abuse,"},{"time":398239,"text":"prostitution in countries where women drive"},{"time":401327,"text":"is higher than countries where women don't drive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404849,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406186,"text":"I know, I was like this, I was shocked."},{"time":407689,"text":"I was like, \"We are the last country in the world"},{"time":410809,"text":"where women don't drive.\""},{"time":412762,"text":"So if you look at the map of the world,"},{"time":414928,"text":"that only leaves two countries:"},{"time":416621,"text":"Saudi Arabia, and the other society is the rest of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421007,"text":"We started a hashtag on Twitter mocking the study,"},{"time":424095,"text":"and it made headlines around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426563,"text":"[BBC News: 'End of virginity' if women drive, Saudi cleric warns]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":428327,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429592,"text":"And only then we realized it's so empowering"},{"time":432263,"text":"to mock your oppressor."},{"time":433727,"text":"It strips it away of its strongest weapon: fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438226,"text":"This system is based on ultra-conservative"},{"time":441830,"text":"traditions and customs"},{"time":443737,"text":"that deal with women as if they are inferior"},{"time":446984,"text":"and they need a guardian to protect them,"},{"time":449481,"text":"so they need to take permission from this guardian,"},{"time":451685,"text":"whether verbal or written, all their lives."},{"time":453851,"text":"We are minors until the day we die."},{"time":456307,"text":"And it becomes worse when it's enshrined in religious fatwas"},{"time":460213,"text":"based on wrong interpretation of the sharia law,"},{"time":462915,"text":"or the religious laws."},{"time":465105,"text":"What's worst, when they become codified"},{"time":467230,"text":"as laws in the system,"},{"time":469681,"text":"and when women themselves believe in their inferiority,"},{"time":473077,"text":"and they even fight those who try"},{"time":475567,"text":"to question these rules."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479137,"text":"So for me, it wasn't only about these attacks I had to face."},{"time":483403,"text":"It was about living two totally different"},{"time":486217,"text":"perceptions of my personality, of my person --"},{"time":489177,"text":"the villain back in my home country,"},{"time":491889,"text":"and the hero outside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493912,"text":"Just to tell you, two stories happened in the last two years."},{"time":497987,"text":"One of them is when I was in jail."},{"time":500365,"text":"I'm pretty sure when I was in jail,"},{"time":502023,"text":"everyone saw titles in the international media"},{"time":506474,"text":"something like this during these nine days I was in jail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510519,"text":"But in my home country, it was a totally different picture."},{"time":513996,"text":"It was more like this:"},{"time":515665,"text":"\"Manal al-Sharif faces charges of disturbing public order"},{"time":518697,"text":"and inciting women to drive.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":522439,"text":"I know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525473,"text":"\"Manal al-Sharif withdraws from the campaign.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":527522,"text":"Ah, it's okay. This is my favorite."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530089,"text":"\"Manal al-Sharif breaks down and confesses:"},{"time":532486,"text":"'Foreign forces incited me.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":534298,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536657,"text":"And it goes on, even trial and flogging me in public."},{"time":541854,"text":"So it's a totally different picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545282,"text":"I was asked last year to give a speech"},{"time":547054,"text":"at the Oslo Freedom Forum."},{"time":549666,"text":"I was surrounded by this love"},{"time":552251,"text":"and the support of people around me,"},{"time":554386,"text":"and they looked at me as an inspiration."},{"time":556571,"text":"At the same time, I flew back to my home country,"},{"time":559433,"text":"they hated that speech so much."},{"time":561358,"text":"The way they called it: a betrayal to the Saudi country"},{"time":563897,"text":"and the Saudi people,"},{"time":565489,"text":"and they even started a hashtag called #OsloTraitor on Twitter."},{"time":568850,"text":"Some 10,000 tweets were written in that hashtag,"},{"time":572119,"text":"while the opposite hashtag, #OsloHero,"},{"time":574937,"text":"there was like a handful of tweets written."},{"time":576721,"text":"They even started a poll."},{"time":578661,"text":"More than 13,000 voters answered this poll:"},{"time":581944,"text":"whether they considered me a traitor or not after that speech."},{"time":584970,"text":"Ninety percent said yes, she's a traitor."},{"time":587996,"text":"So it's these two totally different perceptions"},{"time":591886,"text":"of my personality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593493,"text":"For me, I'm a proud Saudi woman,"},{"time":595517,"text":"and I do love my country,"},{"time":597116,"text":"and because I love my country, I'm doing this."},{"time":600045,"text":"Because I believe a society will not be free"},{"time":602910,"text":"if the women of that society are not free."},{"time":605453,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":615382,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":617734,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":620550,"text":"Thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you."},{"time":623174,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":635938,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639615,"text":"But you learn lessons from these things that happen to you."},{"time":643836,"text":"I learned to be always there."},{"time":646054,"text":"The first thing, I got out of jail,"},{"time":648292,"text":"of course after I took a shower, I went online,"},{"time":651612,"text":"I opened my Twitter account and my Facebook page,"},{"time":654831,"text":"and I've been always very respectful"},{"time":657119,"text":"to those people who are opining to me."},{"time":658626,"text":"I would listen to what they say,"},{"time":660226,"text":"and I would never defend myself with words only."},{"time":663159,"text":"I would use actions. When they said I should withdraw from the campaign,"},{"time":665567,"text":"I filed the first lawsuit against the general directorate"},{"time":668725,"text":"of traffic police for not issuing me a driver's license."},{"time":672967,"text":"There are a lot of people also --"},{"time":674942,"text":"very big support, like those 3,000 people"},{"time":677247,"text":"who signed the petition to release me."},{"time":679611,"text":"We sent a petition to the Shura Council"},{"time":682815,"text":"in favor of lifting the ban on Saudi women,"},{"time":686047,"text":"and there were, like, 3,500 citizens who believed in that"},{"time":689256,"text":"and they signed that petition."},{"time":690889,"text":"There were people like that, I just showed some examples,"},{"time":693760,"text":"who are amazing, who are believing in women's rights in Saudi Arabia,"},{"time":696872,"text":"and trying, and they are also facing a lot of hate"},{"time":699600,"text":"because of speaking up and voicing their views."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703408,"text":"Saudi Arabia today is taking small steps"},{"time":705785,"text":"toward enhancing women's rights."},{"time":707994,"text":"The Shura Council that's appointed by the king,"},{"time":710192,"text":"by royal decree of King Abdullah,"},{"time":712546,"text":"last year there were 30 women assigned to that Council,"},{"time":716154,"text":"like 20 percent."},{"time":718682,"text":"20 percent of the Council. (Applause)"},{"time":721410,"text":"The same time, finally, that Council,"},{"time":723570,"text":"after rejecting our petition four times for women driving,"},{"time":726562,"text":"they finally accepted it last February."},{"time":729137,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":734127,"text":"After being sent to jail"},{"time":735964,"text":"or sentenced lashing, or sent to a trial,"},{"time":738817,"text":"the spokesperson of the traffic police said,"},{"time":740906,"text":"we will only issue traffic violation for women drivers."},{"time":745217,"text":"The Grand Mufti, who is the head"},{"time":746655,"text":"of the religious establishment in Saudi Arabia,"},{"time":749431,"text":"he said, it's not recommended for women to drive."},{"time":753543,"text":"It used to be haram, forbidden, by the previous Grand Mufti."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758073,"text":"So for me, it's not about only these small steps."},{"time":763622,"text":"It's about women themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765187,"text":"A friend once asked me, she said,"},{"time":766839,"text":"\"So when do you think this women driving will happen?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":769590,"text":"I told her, \"Only if women stop asking 'When?'"},{"time":772339,"text":"and take action to make it now.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":775113,"text":"So it's not only about the system,"},{"time":776767,"text":"it's also about us women to drive our own life, I'd say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":783210,"text":"So I have no clue, really, how I became an activist."},{"time":789362,"text":"And I don't know how I became one now."},{"time":793329,"text":"But all I know, and all I'm sure of, in the future"},{"time":796977,"text":"when someone asks me my story,"},{"time":799745,"text":"I will say, \"I'm proud"},{"time":801977,"text":"to be amongst those women who lifted the ban,"},{"time":804833,"text":"fought the ban, and celebrated everyone's freedom.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":808608,"text":"So the question I started my talk with,"},{"time":811905,"text":"who do you think is more difficult to face,"},{"time":815105,"text":"oppressive governments or oppressive societies?"},{"time":818062,"text":"I hope you find clues to answer that from my speech."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820961,"text":"Thank you, everyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822417,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":827185,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":830309,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":835993,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}